channel.title: OK i need some help with this
channel.description: Hello peeps, I've been trying to make a no-ip for a while now. I wanna make one, but I can't figure out where to go to port forward. I know u type in the ip address thing, but it asks for admin acc name and pass. I dont know this because it's my dad's settings. Where can I go to get this info, if i can? Thx for helping.
